df %>%
  select(-Indnum, -Group, -Quality_of_Life_Importance__1_10) %>%
  arrange(Activity) %>%
  filter(!is.na(Consumption)) %>%
  group_by(Activity, Units) %>%
  summarise_all(funs(sum), na.rm = T) %>%
  View(title = "activity and their source source")
sheet1
sheet1 <- sheet1 %>%
  mutate(total_cf = Consumption * rowSums(.[,sources]))
  
sheet1 %>%
group_by(Indnum) %>% 
  summarise(total_QLI = sum(Quality_of_Life_Importance__1_10))
sheet1 %>%
group_by(Indnum) %>% 
  summarise(total_CI = sum(total_cf))
